'''Johann Sebastian Bach''' (* wazaka 21. <span>Marichi</span> <sup>Jul.</sup> <span>/</span> <span style="margin-left:-.1em">31</span> <span style="margin-left:-.1em">Marichi&nbsp;1685 <sup>greg.</sup></span> ku Eisenach, Saxony-Eisenach ; † 28. July 1750 mu Leipzig, Kursachsen) anali woyimba wamkulu waku [[Germany]] munthawi ya Baroque. Bach amadziwika kuti ndi m'modzi mwa oimba wofunikira kwambiri ku Europe. Adakopa oyimba pambuyo pake monga Mozart, Beethoven ndi Brahms, komanso adaimba nyimbo zambiri. Kupanga kwa Bach ndi chimodzi mwazabwino kwambiri m'mbiri ya nyimbo.

Bach adabadwira ku Eisenach mu 1685. Adaphunzitsidwa kusewera zeze ndi bambo ake, a Johann Ambrosius, woliza lipenga kukhothi potumikira Kalonga wa Eisenach. Mnyamata Johann anali asanakwanitse zaka khumi bambo ake atamwalira, kumusiya wamasiye. Anapita kukakhala ndi mchimwene wake wamkulu, a Johann Christoph, omwe amakhala ku Ohrdruf. Chifukwa cha mawu ake oyimba bwino, Bach adapeza udindo ku nyumba ya amonke ku Michaelis ku Lüneberg mu 1700. Liwu lake lidasinthiratu, koma adapitiliza kuyimba zida. Atagwira ntchito kwakanthawi ku Weimar mu 1703 ngati woyimba zeze, Bach adakhala katswiri ku Neue Kirche ku Arnstadt (1703-1707). Ubale wake ndi khonsolo yamatchalitchi udali wovuta popeza woimbayo wachinyamata nthawi zambiri amapeputsa maudindo ake, posankha kuyimba limba. Nkhani ina imafotokoza za tchuthi cha miyezi inayi chomwe adapatsa Bach, kuti apite ku Lubeck komwe akadziwitse nyimbo za Dietrich Buxtehude. Anabwerera ku Arnstadt patadutsa nthawi yomwe amayembekezeredwa ndipo zidakhumudwitsa khonsolo. Kenako adatumikira mwachidule ku St. Blasius ku Mühlhausen ngati wolemba zida, kuyambira mu Juni 1707, ndipo adakwatirana ndi msuweni wake, Maria Barbara Bach, yemwe agwa. Bach adalemba Toccata yake yotchuka ndi Fugue mu D yaying'ono (BWV 565) ndi ma cantata ake oyamba ali ku Mühlhausen, koma mwachangu adapitilira zida zanyumba. Kenako adatenga udindo wa Duke wa Sachsen-Weimar mu 1708, wogwira ntchito ngati khothi komanso wosewera mu orchestra, pomaliza pake adakhala mtsogoleri wawo mu 1714. Adalemba nyimbo zingapo nthawi imeneyi, kuphatikiza Orgel-Büchlein. Chifukwa cha ndale pakati pa a Duke ndi akuluakulu ake, Bach adachoka ku Weimar ndikupeza udindo mu Disembala 1717 ngati Kapellmeister ku Cöthen. Mu 1720, mkazi wa Bach adamwalira mwadzidzidzi, ndikumusiya ndi ana anayi (ena atatu adamwalira ali aang'ono). Posakhalitsa, adakumana ndi mkazi wake wachiwiri, Anna Magdalena Wilcke, yemwe adakwatirana naye mu Disembala 1721. Adzabala ana 13, ngakhale asanu okha ndi omwe adzapulumuke ali mwana. Mabungwe asanu ndi limodzi a Brandenburg Concertos (BWV 1046-51), pakati pazantchito zina zambiri, adayamba zaka zake ku Cöthen. Bach adakhala Kantor wa Thomas School ku Leipzig mu Meyi 1723 ndipo adakhala pampandowu mpaka atamwalira. Anali ku Leipzig komwe adalemba zambiri za zipembedzo zake zachipembedzo komanso zadziko. Bach pamapeto pake sanakhutire ndi ntchitoyi, osati chifukwa chopeza ndalama zochepa, komanso chifukwa chantchito yolemetsa komanso malo osakwanira. Chifukwa chake, adayamba ntchito zina, wamkulu pakati pawo anali oyang'anira mzindawo, gulu la akatswiri oimba komanso ochita masewera omwe ankapereka makonsati sabata iliyonse, mu 1729. Adakhalanso woyang'anira nyimbo ku Dresden Court mu 1736, potumikira Frederick Augusto Wachiwiri; ngakhale ntchito zake zinali zosamveka komanso zowerengeka, zimamupatsa ufulu wolemba zomwe akufuna. Bach adayamba ulendo wopita ku Berlin m'ma 1740, osatinso chifukwa mwana wake, Carl Philipp Emanuel, anali woyimba milandu kumeneko. Mu Meyi 1747, wolemba nyimboyo adalandiridwa ndi manja awiri ndi King Frederick II waku Prussia, yemwe adamulembera zopereka zoyimbira (BWV 1079). Mwa ntchito zomaliza za Bach panali Mass yake ya 1749 ku B minor. Atadwala matenda ashuga, adamwalira pa Julayi 28, 1750.
